Disclaimer regarding Thunderbolt(TM) Linux Software
===================================================

Current source code presented in this github is under
development and intended to facilitate
integration in the future for customers deploying 
Thunderbolt on Linux.

However, at this stage, the kernel code hasn't been accepted
upstream, and therefore might still significantly change. 
Daemon and other components code might significantly change as well. 

Intel team cannot ensure backward compatibility in future releases, 
major changes in design and code for all the components 
presented in this github.

Therefore, the current code is provided AS IS and at your own risk.
Intel will not endorse any responsibility for any kind of integration,
developments, testing, design changes or malfunction that may appear 
due to the changes in any of the presented components. 

Intel Thunderbolt Software Team